208 Section 3. Section 37-1-54.1 is added to the Code of
209 Alabama 1975, to read as follows:
210 §37-1-54.1
211 Consistent with its authority under this chapter, the
212 commission shall establish, adopt, or implement requirements
213 as necessary to ensure that all lobbying expenses are
214 appropriately charged under the commission's system of
215 accounts in such a manner that those expenses are not charged
216 to ratepayers.
